-- Sino-Forest May Seek Company’s Sale, Files for Bankruptcy
-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 2012-03-30T16:21:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-30/sino-forest-may-seek-sale-of-company-files-for-bankruptcy.html
Sino-Forest Corp. (TRE)  said it plans
either a sale of the company or a restructuring under which
noteholders would acquire substantially all of its assets.  The company filed for approval for a court-supervised
restructuring process to stay some creditor claims and start a
sale process.    To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  